\c 137
\s Kuchema kwavakatapwa
\p
\v 1 Panzizi dzeBhabhironi,
\p
\v 13 Ndipo patakagara pasi,
\s zvirokwazvo tikachema, Pakurangarira kwedu Zioni.
\p
\v 2 Pamikonachando mukati madzo Takaturika mbira dzedu.
\p
\v 3 Nokuti ipapo avo vakatitapa vakakumbira
\s kwatiri mashoko orwiyo, Vakatiparadza vakakumbira mufaro, vachiti,
\s "Tiimbireiwo rwiyo rwelioni."
\p
\v 4 Tingaimba seiko rwiyo rwaJehovha Munyika yavatorwa?
\p
\v 5 Kana ndikakukanganwa, iwe Jerusaremu,
\s Ruoko rwangu rworudyi ngarukanganwe
\s umhizha hwarwo.
\p
\v 6 Rurimi rwangu ngarunamatire kumatadzo angu,
\s Kana ndikarega kukurangarira; Kana ndisingati Jerusaremu Ndiwo mufaro wangu mukuru unopfuura zvose.
\p
\v 7 Rangarirai Jehovha, murove vana vaEdhomu
\s Pamusoro pezuva reJerusaremu; Ivo, vakati, "Paradzai, paradzai, Kusvikira panheyo dzaro."
\p
\v 8 Iwe mukunda weBhabhironi, iwe unobva woparadzwa;
\s Munhu uyo achava nomufaro, achakutsivira
\s Sezvawakatiitira iwe.
\p
\v 9 Munhu uyo achava nomufaro, achatora pwere dzako Nokudzirovera padombo.
